  "remarks": "KPi.050 Pak To Chun is a former Secretary of Munitions Industry Department (MID) and currently advises on affairs relating to nuclear and missile programmes. He is a former State Affairs Commission member and is a member Workers’ Party of Korea Political Bureau. Died on 27 July 2022.; Listing: Listed on: 2 Jun. 2017 (amended on 26 Jul. 2022, 16 Aug.2023)",
